<HEAD>Some Communities Cancel Fireworks, But Elsewhere, The Show Goes On</HEAD>
<HEAD>LaserPhoto AX1</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By BART ZIEGLER</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
