<HEAD>Carlucci Announces Suspension Of Contract Payments</HEAD>
<HEAD>LaserPhoto WX6</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By BRYAN BRUMLEY</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
